        <mxCell id="p_cd" style="endArrow=classic;startArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#3B48CC;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="p_vpc_c" target="p_vpc_d">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- Peering features -->
        <mxCell id="p_features" value="特徴&#10;• 推移ルーティング不可 (A→B→C は届かない)&#10;• 接続料金なし、データ転送料のみ&#10;• N個のVPC → N×(N-1)/2 接続が必要&#10;• 4 VPC = 6 接続 / 10 VPC = 45 接続&#10;• CIDR重複 NG (両VPCで非重複が必須)&#10;• リージョン跨ぎ可 (Inter-Region Peering)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontColor=#232F3E;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#3B48CC;strokeWidth=1;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="100" y="430" width="640" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- ===== RIGHT: Transit Gateway ===== -->
        <mxCell id="tgw_box" value="Transit Gateway — ハブ集約 / 推移あり / N接続" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFEFD5;strokeColor=#FF9900;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#232F3E;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="820" y="80" width="720" height="430" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- TGW center icon -->
        <mxCell id="tgw_icon" value="" style="sketch=0;outlineConnect=0;fontColor=#232F3E;gradientColor=none;fillColor=#8C4FFF;strokeColor=#ffffff;dashed=0;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;align=center;html=1;fontSize=12;fontStyle=0;aspect=fixed;shape=mxgraph.aws4.resourceIcon;resIcon=mxgraph.aws4.transit_gateway;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1155" y="240" width="60" height="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="tgw_icon_l" value="Transit Gateway" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#232F3E;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1110" y="305" width="160" height="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- Spoke VPCs -->
        <mxCell id="t_vpc_a" value="VPC A&#10;10.1.0.0/16" style="points=[[0,0],[0.25,0],[0.5,0],[0.75,0],[1,0],[1,0.25],[1,0.5],[1,0.75],[1,1],[0.75,1],[0.5,1],[0.25,1],[0,1],[0,0.75],[0,0.5],[0,0.25]];outlineConnect=0;gradientColor=none;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;container=1;collapsible=0;recursiveResize=0;shape=mxgraph.aws4.group;grIcon=mxgraph.aws4.group_vpc;strokeColor=#248814;fillColor=none;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=30;fontColor=#232F3E;dashed=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="860" y="130" width="140" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_vpc_b" value="VPC B&#10;10.2.0.0/16" style="points=[[0,0],[0.25,0],[0.5,0],[0.75,0],[1,0],[1,0.25],[1,0.5],[1,0.75],[1,1],[0.75,1],[0.5,1],[0.25,1],[0,1],[0,0.75],[0,0.5],[0,0.25]];outlineConnect=0;gradientColor=none;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;container=1;collapsible=0;recursiveResize=0;shape=mxgraph.aws4.group;grIcon=mxgraph.aws4.group_vpc;strokeColor=#248814;fillColor=none;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=30;fontColor=#232F3E;dashed=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1370" y="130" width="140" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_vpc_c" value="VPC C&#10;10.3.0.0/16" style="points=[[0,0],[0.25,0],[0.5,0],[0.75,0],[1,0],[1,0.25],[1,0.5],[1,0.75],[1,1],[0.75,1],[0.5,1],[0.25,1],[0,1],[0,0.75],[0,0.5],[0,0.25]];outlineConnect=0;gradientColor=none;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;container=1;collapsible=0;recursiveResize=0;shape=mxgraph.aws4.group;grIcon=mxgraph.aws4.group_vpc;strokeColor=#248814;fillColor=none;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=30;fontColor=#232F3E;dashed=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="860" y="340" width="140" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_vpc_d" value="VPC D&#10;10.4.0.0/16" style="points=[[0,0],[0.25,0],[0.5,0],[0.75,0],[1,0],[1,0.25],[1,0.5],[1,0.75],[1,1],[0.75,1],[0.5,1],[0.25,1],[0,1],[0,0.75],[0,0.5],[0,0.25]];outlineConnect=0;gradientColor=none;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;container=1;collapsible=0;recursiveResize=0;shape=mxgraph.aws4.group;grIcon=mxgraph.aws4.group_vpc;strokeColor=#248814;fillColor=none;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=30;fontColor=#232F3E;dashed=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1370" y="340" width="140" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- Onprem (extra spoke) -->
        <mxCell id="t_onprem" value="オンプレ&#10;(VPN/DX)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#232F3E;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1115" y="125" width="140" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- TGW spokes -->
        <mxCell id="t_a" style="endArrow=classic;startArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#FF9900;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="t_vpc_a" target="tgw_icon">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_b" style="endArrow=classic;startArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#FF9900;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="t_vpc_b" target="tgw_icon">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_c" style="endArrow=classic;startArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#FF9900;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="t_vpc_c" target="tgw_icon">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_d" style="endArrow=classic;startArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#FF9900;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="t_vpc_d" target="tgw_icon">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="t_o" style="endArrow=classic;startArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#FF9900;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="t_onprem" target="tgw_icon">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- TGW features -->
        <mxCell id="t_features" value="特徴&#10;• 推移ルーティング可 (Route Table で制御)&#10;• N個のVPC → N接続 (TGW Attachment)&#10;• Attachment 料金 ($0.05/h × N) + データ転送料&#10;• Route Table 分離でセグメント化 (本番/開発分離)&#10;• CIDR重複 NG (重複時は PrivateLink/NLB で代替)&#10;• Inter-Region Peering で複数リージョン束ねる" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontColor=#232F3E;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#FF9900;strokeWidth=1;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="860" y="430" width="640" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- ===== Decision Table ===== -->
        <mxCell id="dec_box" value="📊 接続数別の判断早見表" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F5F5F5;strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#232F3E;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="530" width="720" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dec_tbl" value="接続数 (VPC数)        判断              理由&#10;─────────────────────────────────────────&#10; 2〜4 VPC (< 5)       VPC Peering        接続数少、運用シンプル、コスト最安&#10; 5〜9 VPC             ケースバイケース   将来拡張なら TGW、固定なら Peering&#10; 10 VPC 以上 (≥ 10)   Transit Gateway    N×(N-1)/2 が爆発、運用不能&#10;─────────────────────────────────────────&#10;CIDR重複あり          PrivateLink/NLB    Peering/TGW どちらも不可&#10;セグメント分離必要    TGW + Route Table  本番/開発を別RTで隔離&#10;オンプレ含む          TGW                VPN/DX をハブに集約" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontColor=#232F3E;fontFamily=Courier New;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="80" y="560" width="690" height="135" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- ===== Decision Tree ===== -->
        <mxCell id="dec_box2" value="📌 試験で迷ったときの判断フロー" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF5EB;strokeColor=#FF9900;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=13;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#232F3E;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="820" y="530" width="720" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dec_text" value="• 「3つのVPCを最安で接続」→ VPC Peering (3接続のみ)&#10;• 「10+VPC をフルメッシュで接続」→ Transit Gateway 一択&#10;• 「VPC A→B→C と推移させたい」→ TGW (Peeringは不可)&#10;• 「本番と開発を完全分離しつつTGW共有」→ TGW + 別Route Table&#10;• 「CIDR重複した買収先と接続」→ PrivateLink + NLB (Peering/TGW不可)&#10;• 「複数リージョンの全VPCを束ねる」→ TGW Inter-Region Peering or Cloud WAN&#10;• 「TGWのattachment料金が高い」→ 接続数が少ないなら Peering 検討" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;fontColor=#232F3E;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="840" y="560" width="690" height="135" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <!-- Footer note -->
        <mxCell id="footer" value="※ 接続数が増えるほど Peering の管理コスト (Route Table 更新, Security Group 参照) は線形以上に増加。閾値は経験則で 5〜10 VPC。" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#666666;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="710" width="1480" height="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
